    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Explore The World Of Razgovor</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785950/extras/4b87ddc17e5950cf916049673844fef5.avif?t=1766111198\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razgovor Online provides many places for you to explore. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are exploring to enjoy the view or looking for new people to meet, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are different locations and different ways to enjoy the open world of Razgovor Online. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Providing you with places such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bonsila Town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonislashire Park</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Minstfield Town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lux Night Club</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Vault Underground</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Create your own experiance</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785950/extras/9186bd35311b2820e28b45f392422daa.avif?t=1766111198\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razgovor provides in game stores for players to customise their character to look </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >however they want to look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With more clothes being added in the future there will be no shortage of new ways to look.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With Clothing Stores Such as:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > UNLOCKED</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cyber Genesis</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > HuntersRU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Razhair</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Find Your Community</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785950/extras/78cc6505eb6e252754910a51043cd560.avif?t=1766111198\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Razgovor is an inclusive game for all kind of players and provides an open and welcome </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >experiance.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wheather youre looking to Roleplay of just Socialize with others, Razgovor provides tones </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >of ways to share your experiance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Mini Games and Activities</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785950/extras/adb00eeda4f0faa72829346547544f22.avif?t=1766111198\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy Mini-Games with the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each Mini Game includes ways for you to interact with others or with friends without </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >feeling limited to the Main world of Razgovor Online.</p>",
